name: Regret
description:
This photo is the result of my contemplation about life, about the reminder of death, dying with regrets because during life did not do anything and then forgotten, or creating a work that is honest and will continue to speak.

My first collage work, made in 2016. It is a combination of various alternative photography (photogram, lumens) sprinkled with real earth, real flowers, razor strokes, and scanography.
